Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到黑龙竟然和「Fang」勾结在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追击队还没准备好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编队得花些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  我们去救萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  对方可是黑龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们能对抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来你还动不了才对  真是够顽强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气的表情也很美啊  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是药  喝下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你让人绑架我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  毫无戒备地跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一被人类抓到你该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你监视着我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为红龙的结界太坚固  我进不去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让你做我的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是黑龙一族代代相传的婚约之证
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西有着契约之力  只有我能拆掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的所在地也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摆了一道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲斐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发信器  做好迎击准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尼基斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要我做新娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想和你订下契约
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是让龙之力真正觉醒的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有与真心信任的人才能进行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  可以得到压倒一切的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是已经很强了吗  为什么还想要力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到所有遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是龙的追求  你不能理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的东西只有一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想跟你订契约  放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会成为一个好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我城里来吧  碍事的人是进不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那慢慢培养感情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是打算就这样不了了之？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着萝丝不管？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子姐还不是要把萝丝交给「Society」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不一样  我们被萝丝救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:05:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是不明白那孩子自愿跟奥尼基斯走的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了保护我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是为了保护你的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心很痛吧  那是因为萝丝不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再好好考虑一下吧  萝丝的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这个蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候  我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被萝丝救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把萝丝救回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想救她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那就说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说龙司不帮忙的话  我也想不出救萝丝的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想到什么办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪来的密码？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的是S级的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我完全用不上的特级道具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面也有着被诅咒的东西  你害怕再次暴走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  老实说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟第一次接触就那情况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你7岁时做感应测试用的「SLASH BREATH」  打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你能打开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的双亲在「Society」将它登录成了你的专用遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他们为此付出了不少努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜之前收集的遗物几乎全都寄赠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事  我当时可是没有试出任何反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们相信龙司一定能用好它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SLASH BREATH」是用龙牙制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟黑龙战斗就只能用它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道它拥有多大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你能再试一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝之所以会知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为当时爸爸他们来救我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要激发藏在剑中的宝物  集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  想感谢她救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想为伤害了她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想再一次见到她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  借给我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:08:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解  我马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司…龙司！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是红龙  雾的效果已经散去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回龙司的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要龙司以外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就杀了他好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么喜欢他  那就把他的头摘给你好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要杀龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了他吧  人类和龙是绝对无法共存的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们对自己以外的种族存有偏见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司不是那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他对你示爱了吗  说过喜欢你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类讨厌龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们有着毁灭世界的力量  他们害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人  龙司和英理子都很善良
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可结果你还不是被带去「Society」了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不想让你在身边  嫌你碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃他吧  要不我就去杀了他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尼基斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有疑似「Society」的直升机接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信号源  最终反应地点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新东京泛用电波塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的任务是夺回实验对象  可照顾不到你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用您担心  我们是去救萝丝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位都友好点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  最危险的不就是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对研究来说可是不可多得的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计器异常  计器异常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法接近新东京泛用电波塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其周边发生着未知磁场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙的结界吧  果然是还在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由空中入侵不太现实  先降落到地面…唔？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计器恢复  磁场消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  挺厉害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我只是想着要救萝丝  它就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这塔里没有其他人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经装修完毕  但是还没对外开放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个做为暂定基地的好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音感应雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是千钧一发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大概是龙鳞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候混进来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到  塔的中央有一股强大的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是萝丝  还是奥尼基斯  还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意真方便啊  你也越来越熟悉它了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得  萝丝之所以粘上龙司…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  印刻效应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是一见钟情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上了小时候的龙司  想见你所以才到这来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙类哪有这样的感情侧面…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能确定没有吗  见过萝丝之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲斐那家伙  干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该我问你才对  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是订契约前的气氛渲染吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙类竟然会有这种习性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了我明白了  那就由公主亲自跟他说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  跟英理子一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  不要再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事  你们只会把我们当实验材料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也只会把你们当下等生物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙和龙在一起才是最好的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他说得明白些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道人类讨厌龙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌人类  也讨厌龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌讨厌  非常讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我  喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝也喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  喜欢你喜欢你喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你喜欢你喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻舞  冰雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你保护好萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首饰就是婚约的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种烂剑怎么可能打得开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚约解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太嚣张了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够  你应该还有更强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个还给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  重新斟酌下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类怎么可能跟龙在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不会得到幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运让我们战斗  厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些跟我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Engage
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有话跟她说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙的吐息  能治愈人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用拍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我其实是本本族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么忙都帮不上  就老实开车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你  喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝  看够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  我在这下车
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我在一起  奥尼基斯又会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又找不到尸体  大概还没死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给龙司添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  或许他会再来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要变得更强  强到可以在萝丝身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在萝丝身边  所以才不是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能跟我在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  龙司好喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你喜欢你喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  该谁去负责解释啊？
